    "Interest in measuring and improving specifications seems to be on an upward trend, considering we only sampled papers up to July 2023.",
    "Computer vision is present in about half of papers, followed by natural language processing.",
    "Only 12% of the papers explore other application areas (e.g., graph and tabular data).",
    "As a last step, we select the five most cited papers 5 from each application area for each year.",
    "That was done to keep the workload of analyzing papers manageable while keeping impactful papers and maintaining coverage of different years and application areas."
